  "text": "In addition, control plates containing Min (a concentration of 10 × IC 50 of Cpd-17), Max (DMSO), and reference (a concentration of IC 50 of Cpd-17) wells were included in the runs to establish the Z′ factor. 7, [CITATION_1] An overall screening Z′ factor of ~0.6 was achieved, demonstrating that the assay's performance is robust and suitable for application in an HTS campaign.",
